    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who are expert in one or more of the group of studies or branches of knowledge concerned with facts and phenomena of the observable or quantifiable world, and who employ the scientific method in their work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
